<html lang='en'>
  <head>
    <meta charset='UTF-8' />
    <meta http-equiv='X-UA-Compatible' content='IE=edge' />
    <meta name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0' />
    <link
      href='https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css'
      rel='stylesheet'
      integrity='sha384-rbsA2VBKQhggwzxH7pPCaAqO46MgnOM80zW1RWuH61DGLwZJEdK2Kadq2F9CUG65'
      crossorigin='anonymous'
    />
    <link rel="icon" href="images/logo.jpg" type="image/icon type">
    <title>Vesire - Cùng bạn đi mọi nẻo đường</title>
    <script src='https://kit.fontawesome.com/8d62a64fa1.js' crossorigin='anonymous'></script>
    <link rel='preconnect' href='https://fonts.googleapis.com' />
    <link rel='stylesheet' href='/stylesheets/style.css' />
    <link rel='stylesheet' href='/stylesheets/layouts/home.css' />
    <link rel='stylesheet' href='/stylesheets/layouts/main.css' />
    <link rel='stylesheet' href='/stylesheets/layouts/booking.css' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <header class='main__header'>
      <img src='/images/bg_main.png' alt='' width='100%' />
      <div class='main__menu'>
        <h4 class='mb-0'>VESIRE</h4>
        <div class='main__menu__item main__menu__item--active rounded-pill'>
          <i class='fa-solid fa-house'></i>
        </div>
        <div class='main__menu__item rounded-pill'>
          <i class='fa-solid fa-car-tunnel'></i>
        </div>
        <div class='main__menu__item rounded-pill'>
          <i class='fa-solid fa-circle-question'></i>
        </div>
        <div class='main__account rounded-pill ms-auto'>
          <img
            src='https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/149/149071.png'
            alt=''
            width='30'
            height='30'
          />
          <div class='fw-medium ms-2 me-3'>Cái Minh Chánh</div>
          <i class='fa-solid fa-arrow-right-from-bracket fs-5'></i>
        </div>
      </div>
    </header>

    <div class='container' style='min-height: 100vh;'>
      <div class="search">
      {{{body}}}
      {{#each busTrips}}
      {{! item mỗi chuyến xe }}
      <div class='rounded bg-white text-center mt-3 mx-auto px-4 py-3'>
        <div class='d-flex'>
          <div>
            <div class='text-start'>
              <span class='me-3 ps-1 pe-3'>Rẻ nhất</span>
              <span>Đánh giá: <span class='text-warning'>{{this.rating}}</span></span>
            </div>
            <hr class='mt-1 mb-4' />
            <div class='d-flex align-items-center'>
              <img src='/images/logo nhà xe.png' alt='' class='px-1' />
              <span class='fw-semibold ps-2 pe-5'>{{this.brandName}}</span>

              <div class='d-inline-block'><p class='mb-1 fw-bolder fs-5'>{{this.goTime}}</p><span
                >Quảng Ninh</span></div>
              <img src='/images/thanh hành trình.png' alt='' class='px-1 pb-4' />
              <div class='d-inline-block'><p
                  class='mb-1 fw-bolder fs-5'
                >{{this.arriveTime}}</p><span>Quảng Ninh</span></div>
              <span class='px-4 fw-bolder'>{{this.totalHours}}</span>
              <span class='bg-secondary bg-opacity-25 rounded-pill px-4 py-1'>Chi tiết</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class='d-flex flex-column justify-content-center ps-5 ms-5'>
            <p class='fs-4 fw-bold py-0 mb-0'>{{this.price}}<span
                class='text-secondary fs-6 fw-lighter'
              >VNĐ</span></p>
            <span class='d-block ps-3 mb-3'>Có voucher</span>
            <a href='/booking' class='btn btn-primary d-block px-4'>
              ĐẶT NGAY
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    {{/each}}
      <div class = "filter">
        <h3>Bộ lọc</h3>
        <div class="filter-body">
          <div class = "filter-price">
            <div>Price</div>
              <div>+795</div>
          </div>
          <div class ="filter-chart">Biểu đồ</div>
          <label class ="hangxelabel"for="Hãng xe">Hãng xe</label>
          <select name="Hãng xe" id="Hãng xe">
            <option value="Mai Linh">Mai Linh</option>
            <option value="Mai Linh">Mai Linh</option>
            <option value="Mai Linh">Mai Linh</option>
            <option value="Mai Linh">Mai Linh</option>
          </select>
          <div class="rating-label">Rating</div>
          <div class="rating">
            <div class="ratingcheckbox">
              <input type="checkbox" id="rating1" name="rating1" value="1">
              <label for="rating1"> 1 sao</label><br>
            </div>
            <div class="ratingcheckbox">
              <input type="checkbox" id="rating2" name="rating2" value="2">
              <label for="rating2"> 2 sao</label><br>
            </div>
            <div class="ratingcheckbox">
              <input type="checkbox" id="rating3" name="rating3" value="3">
              <label for="rating3"> 3 sao</label><br>
            </div>
            <div class="ratingcheckbox">
              <input type="checkbox" id="rating4" name="rating4" value="4">
              <label for="rating4"> 4 sao</label><br>
            </div>
            <div class="ratingcheckbox">
              <input type="checkbox" id="rating5" name="rating5" value="5">
              <label for="rating5"> 5 sao</label><br>
            </div>
              
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
    <footer class='home__footer'>
      <div class='home__footer__content'>
        <div class='home__footer__section'>
          <div class='home__footer__title'>VERSIRE</div>
          <div>
            Được thành lập từ năm 2022, VESIRE đã xây dựng được tên tuổi trong lĩnh vực thương mại
            điện tử, công nghệ và du lịch. VESIRE tự hào mang lại cho khách hàng trải nghiệm đặt vé
            & phương tiện thông minh cho hành khách, phần mềm quản lý hiệu quả cho nhà xe
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class='home__footer__section'>
          <div class='home__footer__title'>Hỗ trợ</div>
          <div>
            <a href='#'>Hướng dẫn đặt vé</a>
            <a href='#'>Điều khoản & điều kiện</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class='home__footer__section'>
          <div class='home__footer__title'>Theo dõi</div>
          <div>
            <div class='d-flex gap-2 align-items-center'>
              <i class='fa-brands fa-facebook'></i>
              <div>Facebook</div>
            </div>
            <div class='d-flex gap-2 align-items-center'>
              <i class='fa-solid fa-phone'></i>
              <div>Hotline: 0123.456.789</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class='home__footer__copy-right'>
        © Copyright 2022, All Rights Reserved by ClarityUI
      </div>
    </footer>

    <script
      src='https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@popperjs/core@2.11.6/dist/umd/popper.min.js'
      integrity='sha384-oBqDVmMz9ATKxIep9tiCxS/Z9fNfEXiDAYTujMAeBAsjFuCZSmKbSSUnQlmh/jp3'
      crossorigin='anonymous'
    ></script>
    <script
      src='https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.3/dist/js/bootstrap.min.js'
      integrity='sha384-cuYeSxntonz0PPNlHhBs68uyIAVpIIOZZ5JqeqvYYIcEL727kskC66kF92t6Xl2V'
      crossorigin='anonymous'
    ></script>
  </body>
</html>